OL,6,FIt happened in the 1970s and 1980s,
OL,7,Fand after decades of campaiging for
OL,8,Fjustice, victims and their families
OL,9,Fwill finally get answers in a
OL,10,Fmilestone report out on Monday after a
OL,11,Fsix year long inquiry.
OL,13,FHere, ITV News explains everything you
OL,14,Fneed to know about the infected blood
OL,15,Fscandal.
OL,17,FWhat was the infected blood scandal?
