OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What was it -
OL,4,Cand who was affected?
OL,6,FIn the US, donors were paid to give
OL,7,Ftheir blood, and were often prisoners
OL,8,Fand drug addicts, many of whom had
OL,9,Fdeadly viruses like HIV and Hepatitis
OL,10,FC.
OL,12,FThe blood donated was then pooled
OL,13,Ftogether to make the drugs, which
OL,14,Fmeant entire batches were often
OL,15,Fcontaminated.
OL,17,FThere were numerous warnings about the
OL,18,Fimported blood and the risks, but the
OL,19,FUK was unable to produce the amounts
OL,20,Fof blood it needed, so carried on
OL,21,Fimporting it from abroad.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/14
