OL,6,FPatients also say they weren't
OL,7,Fproperly warned about the dangers of
OL,8,Fthe products.
OL,10,FOne shocking case saw boys with
OL,11,Fhaeomophilia tested on with the
OL,12,Fproducts without their knowledge.
OL,14,FEighty haemophiliacs at Treolar's
OL,15,FBoy's School, in Hampshire, were given
OL,16,Finfected blood products as part of
OL,17,Ftheir treatment, and only 16 are still
OL,18,Falive today.
