OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What was it -
OL,4,Cand who was affected?
OL,6,FIt's heard testimony from hundreds of
OL,7,Fwitnesses and reviewed thousands of
OL,8,Fdocuments. The key questions to be
OL,9,Fanswered are: who knew what and when,
OL,10,Fand where the responsibilities for the
OL,11,Fscandal lie.
OL,13,FSome of the witnesses include senior
OL,14,Fpoliticians - including former prime
OL,15,Fminister Sir John Major, current Prime
OL,16,FMinister Rishi Sunak, and former
OL,17,Fhealth secretaries Jeremy Hunt and
OL,18,FAndy Burnham.
