OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What was it -
OL,4,Cand who was affected?
OL,6,FMultiple key documents in government
OL,7,Farchives are either missing or were
OL,8,Fdestroyed, which has led some
OL,9,Fcampaigners to suggest there was an
OL,10,Fattempt to cover up the scandal.
OL,12,FThe inquiry's final report had been
OL,13,Fexpected in autumn last year, but the
OL,14,Fchair, Sir Brian Langstaff, said he
OL,15,Fneeded more time to prepare "a report
OL,16,Fof this gravity".
