OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: What was it -
OL,4,Cand who was affected?
OL,6,FMany of those who were infected had to
OL,7,Fgive up their jobs and live on
OL,8,Fbenefits because of health problems.
OL,10,FIn July 2022, Sir Brian made his first
OL,11,Fformal recommendation that victims
OL,12,Fshould be given interim compensation
OL,13,Fpayments of #100,000 each.
OL,15,FThere were 4,000 eligible survivors
OL,16,Fand families who received the payments.
OL,18,FIt's estimated the cost of
OL,19,Fcompensation will run into billions,
OL,20,Fsomewhere between #4 billion and #20
OL,21,Fbillion.
